race.description: Beeline Car & Truck Wash Mdn Plate
race.comment: LAYIN' UP (7) returns and looks ready to strike after seven placings from 10 starts. Trialled sharply and draws well for Crowther. This looks her chance. NINA'S COMET (8) debuts for the Theodore yard and impressed in her latest trial, scoring with something in hand. Expecting a bright start. SILENT LEGACY (4) also debuts and won his most recent trial. Draws well and gets in light with the 2kg claim. Market push expected. GAZELLE (10) was solid on debut at Penola, finishing third. Open to good improvement and Milnes sticks. EXCUSE FORA PARTY (6) has shown promise in her trials and draws to get every chance. Have to respect.
